# End-to-end test: compile C, generate JVM impl, run main and verify output.
# Single-pass compile: the plugin's ffiGenerate eagerly materializes TASTy via the
# bundled Scala 3 compiler when no class-directory TASTy exists yet, so a single
# `compile` produces a runnable build.
> ffiCompile
> ffiPackage
> compile
> run
